{"tid":2362884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那01新聞部員工初步確診武肺","createTime":"2021-01-11T18:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T02:00:36.000Z","uid":39521,"like":98,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"590f4198a1e2c3986748661cdaf24882b6a62a90","tid":2362884,"uid":39521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T18:47:05.000Z","msg":"香港01新聞部今天（1月12日）接獲一名同事報告，初步確診新型冠狀病毒，現正接受治療。該同事工作的樓層，以及本公司的其他樓層，已經即時進行徹底清潔和消毒。<br />\n<br />\n 香港01將會按照衞生署指示，安排相關同事在檢測無礙後，方才重新參與新聞工作。<br />\n香港01為保障全體員工健康，將安排相關所有同事盡可能在家工作，並安排有關同事接受新型冠狀病毒檢測。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SGHJ5pp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSGHJ5pp.png&h=63165e2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1b2c6437d1b2a921d3008913423b14e766ba5f","tid":2362884,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T18:47:36.000Z","msg":"皇"},{"pid":"8dfaab04785d8c14ac5387edf5a6082075242e55","tid":2362884,"uid":88743,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T18:49:03.000Z","msg":"樓下千祈唔好打飛機<br />\n死左先好開香檳唔該"},{"pid":"9d9c49d0c1368a5dbb159f4d338900e29a7115cb","tid":2362884,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T22:11:25.000Z","msg":"好撚嘢"},{"pid":"d1f7cf4d5bd111fde9ba67ec441c8a4c2ffff2dd","tid":2362884,"uid":388055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T22:12:59.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"25057b159cc5beafc1a93088c210ac3607d0cfe7","tid":2362884,"uid":254535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T22:20:07.000Z","msg":"快d傳染比高層"},{"pid":"f29433132ea6e853dde244506a4b4767b4ba58fa","tid":2362884,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T22:26:01.000Z","msg":"報應不爽"},{"pid":"52385a948b2349957a7233b533fe0cdc3654abe2","tid":2362884,"uid":264426,"like":1,"dislik